                            <comment id="16840909" author="kinow" created="Thu, 16 May 2019 01:44:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One warning in exiftool when validating, regarding a PNG chunk size issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ exiftool -v -validate testfile_2.png
&#160; ExifToolVersion = 10.80
&#160; FileName = testfile_2.png
&#160; Directory = .
&#160; FileSize = 35144
&#160; FileModifyDate = 1557970557
&#160; FileAccessDate = 1557970559
&#160; FileInodeChangeDate = 1557970559
&#160; FilePermissions = 33204
&#160; FileType = PNG
&#160; FileTypeExtension = PNG
&#160; MIMEType = image/png
&#160; Warning = Bad CRC for IHDR chunk
PNG IHDR (13 bytes):
&#160; + [BinaryData directory, 13 bytes]
&#160; | ImageWidth = 398
&#160; | ImageHeight = 249
&#160; | BitDepth = 8
&#160; | ColorType = 6
&#160; | Compression = 0
&#160; | Filter = 157
&#160; | Interlace = 157
&#160; Warning = Invalid PNG chunk size
&#160; Validate = 0 2 0
Validate&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; : 2 Warnings&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16840915" author="kinow" created="Thu, 16 May 2019 01:54:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good catch! It was a boolean logic issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (method &amp;lt; 0 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; method &amp;gt;= InterlaceMethod.values().length) {&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the InterlaceMethods.values().length is 2 at the moment, and the method value was -99, then it was doing:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (-99 &amp;lt; 0 &amp;amp;&amp;amp; -99 &amp;gt;= 2) {&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Which would never evaluate to true. Fixed by changing from &amp;amp;&amp;amp; to ||.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
